          <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
          <li><a href="#tech">Tech Stack</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/resume.pdf"
              style="font-weight: 600"
              download="resume.pdf"
              target="_blank"
            >
              Resume
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download" style="margin-left: 5px"></i>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <section id="about">
        <h2 class="section-title">Front Page Story</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
          <img src="20250426_112652.png" alt="Profile" class="profile-img" />
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              In a world dominated by flashy colors and overwhelming designs, I
              stand apart with a commitment to elegant simplicity. As a
              final-year Computer Science student, I am passionate about
              building clean and meaningful digital experiences.
            </p>
            <p>
              During my academic journey, I have worked on projects that reflect
              both technical skills and creativity. My focus is on web
              development and data structures, where I enjoy solving problems
              and creating solutions that are practical and user-friendly.
            </p>
            <p>
              "I believe in the power of minimalism," I say. "When you strip
              away the unnecessary, what remains is pure, focused functionality.
              That's where true design happens."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="projects">
        <h2 class="section-title">Featured Projects</h2>
        <div class="projects-grid">
          <div class="project-card">
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none; /* removes underline */
                color: inherit;
              "
              href="/projects/shorting_visualizer"
            >
              <img
                src="data:image/png;base64,"
                alt="Project 1"
                class=""
              />
              <h3 class="project-title">The Sorting Visualizer</h3>
              <p class="project-description">
                An interactive sorting visualizer that demonstrates algorithms
                step by step, making learning sorting techniques engaging,
                clear, and intuitive.
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card">
            <img
              src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTJjpHpnrh8l3uc5hxHZLv8AKCrAuEnXJECUg&s"
              alt="Project 3"
              class=" "
            />
            <h3 class="project-title">Black & White Store</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              A To-Do List stores tasks in browser localStorage, enabling
              offline use with persistent add, edit, and delete functionality.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card">
            <img
              src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTpREeseTY2Aa6X8pRvc8B2DmYB7zyQJx7Zqg&s"
              alt="Project 3"
              class=" "
            />
            <h3 class="project-title">Black & White Store</h3>
            <p class="project-description">
              An e-commerce platform that proves you don't need color to create
              an engaging shopping experience. Focuses on product quality and
              user experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="tech" class="tech-stack">
        <h2 class="section-title">Technical Arsenal</h2>
        <div class="tech-grid">
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fab fa-html5 tech-icon"></i>
            <span>HTML5</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fab fa-css3-alt tech-icon"></i>
            <span>CSS3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fab fa-js tech-icon"></i>
            <span>JavaScript</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fab fa-react tech-icon"></i>
            <span>React</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fab fa-node-js tech-icon"></i>
            <span>Node.js</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-item">
            <i class="fas fa-database tech-icon"></i>
            <span>MongoDB</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title">Send a Dispatch</h2>
        <form class="contact-form" method="post" action="/send">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input
              name="email"
              type="email"
              placeholder="Your Email"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <textarea
              name="message"
              placeholder="Your Message"
              required
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message</button>
        </form>
        <div class="thank-you-message" style="display:none; text-align:center; font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:bold; padding:20px;">
